              org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack icon,
              NotEmptyArrayList<KitItem> items)
       throws KitAlreadyExistsException
        Create a new Kit
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the kit - must be unique - for best results use a random string in case of other plugins conflicting
        icon - The ItemStack that will show in the Kit Menu
        items - A list that must contain at least one KitItem to be in the Kit
        Throws:
        KitAlreadyExistsException - if a kit with the given name already exists
